The paper discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning for multi-agent systems, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The focus is on addressing challenges related to multi-agent training schemes (cs.MA), which can involve robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
